{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/Head.jpg?t=1721936907\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/about.jpg?t=1721936907\" /><br>Hi !<br><br>Hexocity is a relaxing puzzle game set up in a futuristic world. Inspired by the great &quot;Dorfromantik&quot; we have decided to make this game to build our team with a limit of 6 months of development.<br><br>Build your archipelago while listening to relaxing synthwave music.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/general.gif?t=1721936907\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/Key_Features.jpg?t=1721936907\" /><br><br>Hexocity is a relaxing puzzle game where you place hexagonal tiles and win points by connecting the same elements.<br><br>You start with a limited number of tiles and the game ends when you reach 0. Some features will allow you to win more tiles so you can extend the game duration.<br>Make the best score before the end!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>PERFECTS</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/Perfect.gif?t=1721936907\" /><br>Make perfect tiles to win powers &amp; a bonus of points and 1 more tile.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>POWERS</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/Powers.gif?t=1721936907\" /><br>Use powers that will be given to you with each perfect :<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Refresh: change the current tile<br></li><li> Generate: select an empty spot and get a tile that fits perfectly<br></li><li> Delete: delete the selected tile.<br></li><li> Copy : copy an existing tile</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>QUESTS</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/quests.gif?t=1721936907\" /><br>Win bonuses of points &amp; tiles with quests.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Connect 2 Roads : place your ending point and place tiles to connect both points. The shortest path gives a bonus.<br></li><li> Connect 2 Canals : Place your ending point and place tiles to connect both points. All tiles give a bonus.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>CREATIVE MODE </strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/Creative01.gif?t=1721936907\" /><br>Create your own islands with no limits in the creative mode.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/Creative02.gif?t=1721936907\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820100/extras/OST.jpg?t=1721936907\" /><br>There is a little more than an hour of original soundtrack in Hexocity, composed by Way16a's composer: Raphael Ledent.<br>Let yourself flow with the relaxing synthwave of Hexocity.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First steps!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2820100/583d1e969ebfce58c491f8c1b43b2400466e2a63.jpg"},{"name":"Builder","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2820100/f9aaede77a0628b5c10efc5ac9dd6dddfd15e8cc.jpg"},{"name":"Observer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2820100/f5d67d60e3c3ed5d7f7e1c184d938ab67164aead.jpg"},{"name":"Champion I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2820100/17085246ecde6bc278f5f78670c0572bff410445.jpg"},{"name":"Champion II","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2820100/74e8cfb9fbbc1f28a34af3dbd2cceb0b2d9e1